Question (Cargo Handling and Decoration System)

Scenario: You are writing a cargo handling system for a logistics company.
In the system, cargoes (BasicPackage) are defined according to their weight and contents.
Customers can add additional labels/attributes to their cargoes dynamically at runtime, such as "Fragile" (FragileDecorator).
These prepared cargoes are then given to a chain of responsibility.
 In the chain, SmallCarrier carries cargoes under 10 kg, while BigCarrier carries cargoes of 10 kg and above.

Design this system using Decorator and Chain of Responsibility patterns. Create the class structure and show how a
 5 kg "Fragile" package is processed by the chain within the Main class.